      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a 3.85 final drive ratio, the powertrain is mechanically flawless. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring peak reliability. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M-Variable differential for surgical handling. Finished with an unblemished carbon fiber roof and a concours-quality interior, this M3 is a turnkey investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
